dcterms:description: The Stanford Drone Dataset (SDD) contains class labels for six different types of agents, including pedestrian, cyclist, cart, car, skater, and bus. Data is captured from a bird’s-eye view by flying a drone over Stanford University’s campus.
dcterms:title: Stanford Drone Dataset (SDD)
